  "title": "Commodities Trader - WCAN",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Lead sales and marketing initiatives within the trading division.</li>\n  <li>Maintain strong relationships with existing clients and actively pursue new business opportunities.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate daily operations with clients, international offices, and company headquarters to ensure smooth workflow.</li>\n  <li>Manage order fulfillment and oversee logistics to guarantee timely deliveries.</li>\n  <li>Track customer credit limits and manage inventory levels effectively.</li>\n  <li>Ensure seamless handling of logistics and payment processes.</li>\n  <li>Welcome and assist overseas visitors, providing a professional and positive experience.</li>\n  <li>Travel within the Asia-Pacific region to meet suppliers and customers as needed.</li>\n  <li>Take on special projects and other responsibilities to support departmental goals.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Qualifications:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum 2–3 years of relevant work experience (sales-related experience preferred).</li>\n  <li>Self-motivated, observant, and eager to learn.</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication and interpersonal skills.</li>\n  <li>Analytical thinker with a positive and solution-oriented attitude.</li>\n  <li>Comfortable engaging with clients and working in an external, field-based environment.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>\n<p>EA Personnel: Nyon Hock Sen (Aden)</p>\n<p>EA Personnel Reg No: R24124070</p>",
